    prompt "EU operation category"
    default REMOTEID_EU_CATEGORY_OPEN
    help
        EU Drone Regulation operation category for the System message.
        Self-built drones without a class label typically operate under
        the Open category rules. Use Specific or Certified only if you
        hold the corresponding authorisation or type certificate.

